== Usage ==
Use this template to inform users that the [[w:Wikipedia|Wikipedia]] encyclop√¶dia has an article on the page you're using the template on, or a related article. You can use this template in three ways:
<pre>{{wikipedia}}</pre>
will link to the Wikipedia article with the current page name: {{wikipedia}}

<pre>{{wikipedia|name}}</pre>
will link to the Wikipedia article named <code>name</code> instead: {{wikipedia|name}}

<pre>{{wikipedia|name|text}}</pre>
will link to the Wikipedia article named <code>name</code> and display the text <code>text</code>: {{wikipedia|name|text}}

[[Category:Templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]
</noinclude>